The paper proposes algorithms for computing winners under tiebreaking mechanisms for two well-studied voting rules, STV and RP. This involves search algorithms, pruning strategies, heuristics, sampling, and machine learning. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), and Game Theory (cs.GT).
